# Desiree 1.0

Entry:

- system 1: long when CLOSE > 20-day high, short when CLOSE < 20-day low
- system 2: long when CLOSE > 55-day high, short when CLOSE < 55-day low

every 0.5ATR(20) add a position up to 4

Exit:

- system 1: close long positions when CLOSE < 10-day low, close short positions when CLOSE > 10-day high
- system 2: close long positions when CLOSE < 20-day low, close short positions when CLOSE > 20-day high

Hard SL: 2ATR(20)
Stops move higher/lower 0.5ATR(20) for every long/short position added

risk 2 % per trade
amount to bet in lots = (risk*account balance) / (SL*contract size)

for the x-day highs/lows we use the Donchain channel indicator
